California consumers can exercise their rights directly or through an authorized agent by contacting us at
privacy@claris.com
or by phone to Claris Customer Support at 1-800-325-2747. Claris may ask you for more information that we consider necessary to verify your identity for security and to prevent fraud. This information may include name, contact information, and information related to your transaction or relationship with Claris, but the specific information requested may differ depending on the circumstances of your request. If we delete your personal information, we will both render certain personal information about you permanently unrecoverable and also deidentify certain personal information.
Do Not Track
Claris does not track its customers over time and across third party websites to provide targeted advertising and therefore does not respond to Do Not Track (DNT) signals. Third parties that have content embedded on Claris’ websites such as a social feature or a stock ticker may set cookies on a user’s browser and/or obtain information about the fact that a web browser visited a specific Claris website from a certain IP address. Third parties cannot collect any other personal information from Claris’ websites unless you provide it to them directly.
